{
  "stem": "14552.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 461.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, you have--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Out of our homes to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Take what you want and go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- that was around Passover.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were told to get our belongings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we would be assigned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had friends living in a-- in a very nice house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave us a room there-- for all of us, one room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we packed our warm clothes, and whatever we could, and went there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we stayed in the ghetto for one month.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And again there they would take people--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the-- the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were-- we took some stuff.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were allowed only once to go back to the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was that time when I really turned to the house for one more-- one more look.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will never forget that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went back, and the house looked so beautiful, and so big, and so-- it wasn't that big, but in my mind it was so big.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the flower garden, which was nothing was done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everything there was just the grass whatever was grown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was just not-- it was a memory I cannot get out of my mind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the last time I said I thought I'll see that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went back in 1968 and I saw it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I have some pictures of it which is dilapidated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we had vines growing over the veranda, and we had the greenery everywhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when I went back in '68, there was nothing growing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No grapevines growing.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
